Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:06.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,衰弱 贫困 贫富差距变大…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,黑暗时代的日本!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:10.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这个看不到未来的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:13.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,女神们降临了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:23.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,用可爱的笑容和歌声 改变这无可救药的日本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:26.77,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她们就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,偶像议员!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:39.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这次真的有劳殿村议员了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:48.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是我一点心意 希望能合您口味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.96,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,看上去挺美味的点心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:59.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,话说越后先生 您下手也够黑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:04.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 不敢和殿村议员您相提并论啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:17.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,议员 议员!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,媒体宣传是心脏病发作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:35.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,直接原因是被食物噎住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:41.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎哟 那人以前就看见好吃的就红眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:44.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对了 那补选的候补人怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不好意思 还没什么眉目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:53.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,老师 要在东京找补选的候选人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,今天去新泻也毫无收获
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:59.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说是要找受当地喜爱孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.94,0:02:02.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也不知要该从何找起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,神代先生 停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:19.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了 现在没有什么空闲时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:27.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,议员 你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:34.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大家 今天也伴着我的歌声下种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:39.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,加把劲下种了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:48.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,呀 今年插秧也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,果然奶奶做的饭团就是好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:01.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,吃的这么急 小心噎着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:06.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,话说回来 夏月还真是喜欢唱歌给别人听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:10.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我们家附近的秧也顺利的插完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 谢谢你的插秧歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,下次也拜托你了 我们村的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎呀 偶像什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:24.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月的歌 能让他人露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:29.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,从小就喜欢唱歌 大家听了你的歌都发自内心的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也长成了这么个好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哇 被夸奖了! 最喜欢奶奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:44.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,想不想让全国人都听到你的歌声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我来做偶像议员?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:51.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话 要不要来参加这次的选拔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我参加 务必让我参…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:58.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,奶奶 水…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以 刚刚和你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事 真是个有活力的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我要成为偶像!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:48.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,下面 开始选举女主角党新泻一区补选的候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:53.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,感谢今天从全国各地赶来的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,选举会场在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哇 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这高坡什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:10.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,直通云霄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:16.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,据说 爬上这高坡的人一定可以赢下第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,传说中的 偶像坡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:22.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,第一个爬上这高坡的人 算是合格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让我看看大家的干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么 预备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:31.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,跑…的时候 就开始比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:45.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,议员 再怎么说这样的选拔也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:49.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么这么说 偶像的身体就是本钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:53.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里就是第一个要越过的坎…开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:58.24,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好累啊 果然成为偶像不是一件容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 GG了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也GG了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:05.71,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,东京竟然有这样的坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:19.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:22.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.56,0:07:23.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,成为偶像!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:25.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,一定要成为偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,爆发了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,成功了! 成功了! 成功了! 成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,奶奶 我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:43.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 怎么了 出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我当上偶像议员了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:47.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哇 可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:51.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真的选那孩子没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:56.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,因为 爬到坡顶的只有她一个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就这随意的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:03.26,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不会吧 日本没有总统吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这可不是搞笑节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 涂出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请您认真考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:14.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,担心过度会秃顶的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事 船到桥头自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:22.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,球过…走过路过的各位 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:28.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是本次女主角党提名的猴选…候选人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我叫星菜夏虐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,紧张的不像样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以我说她担不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:40.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,本来身为偶像议员受到的绯言绯语就够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:42.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,现在还搞什么偶像议员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:43.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.97,0:08:47.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,小妹妹 你当选了我有什么好处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:50.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…我会全力以布…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,女主角党的各位 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是巧合的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,政治要的是力量 是实力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:02.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位不要被外表的光鲜表演给蒙蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请大家为我们楼凯党投上一票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,让我鹭宫成为真正的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.46,0:09:18.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,也请让我变成女人吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:25.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我都告诉她了 偶像禁止男女交往 要注意言行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她这瞎说的话可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,搞砸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:32.23,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这怎么办啊 议员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她也差不多要来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:41.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:45.45,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,太慢啦 等的我都快石化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还以为被放鸽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.41,0:09:53.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,再怎么说也是女主党党首亲自邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.37,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我也不能无视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:00.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.97,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,对的 感觉还不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:09.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幸惠 有时候真看不透你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:12.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸小姐 就是那位鬼丸静小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:17.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,两次当选 要说的话 就是你的前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是 星菜夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:22.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很久以前就是鬼丸小姐的粉丝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:26.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,很久? 别说的我年龄大一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我和你是同龄人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:33.33,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,幸惠 叫我来的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.67,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:43.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不会要让我唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我毕生的请求 好不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你之前也说过这话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:52.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有什么不好的啊 人家就是为了这事才叫你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哪跟哪啊 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.77,0:11:00.11,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就这么放弃了啊 举白旗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:03.65,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,果然静还是无法和新人相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:05.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,可惜啊 明明是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:14.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,她真的是个好孩子哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:19.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我知道了 我干还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:23.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 作为条件 我要用我自己的方式来做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:26.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:31.18,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说白了 你现在还没有和我一起唱歌的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:33.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果想和我一起站在舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.60,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就付出相应的努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:36.93,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我不会放水的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:43.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果我觉得你不合格 就会二话不说甩了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,如果不想这样的话 就拼命跟上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:47.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,明白了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请尽情鞭策我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:53.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,就算吐血变成木乃伊也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,意外的…积极啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:59.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这里 节奏没跟上 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:00.42,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,疼疼…疼 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:04.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,要差的远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:05.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我不会认输的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.63,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,右边 左边 右边 左边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:11.80,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:15.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没事 一点都不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.27,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会认输的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:23.56,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不是声音大就可以了 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:24.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.57,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月真是努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,全力以赴 我没说错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还在在意那件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:43.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:47.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,今天的训练到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:49.84,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:52.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你没有和我站在同一个舞台上的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.64,0:12:55.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,仅仅是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:11.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,传单我看了 一定会去演唱会给你们加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:16.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,能和那个鬼丸静小姐搭档真是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:20.12,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,今天有农活所以没去看训练
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 演唱会时全村的人都会去捧场的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,喂 夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:36.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,把我从踢出成员?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:50.19,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我的表演是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:58.70,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,确实你的表演是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.29,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,拥有着超人的才华
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:04.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是你的光环
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:12.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你的光环伤害了太多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:17.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你的光环是无法和人融合的双刃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:31.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,双刃剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:39.91,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:41.79,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样啊 担心那孩子特地来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那 夏月现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.25,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别勉强啊 夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:54.55,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不稍微休息一下 身体会垮掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:56.38,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没关系 我还可以坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.43,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还可以坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:02.68,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我不甘心 不想就这么放过自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:05.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么努力的指导我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:10.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,为我一人 流了那么多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:12.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:17.20,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,没有回应她的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:21.62,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.20,0:15:24.16,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我不得不去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.46,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不得不做!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.96,0:15:32.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:36.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说的好!加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:39.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎呀 看来是我多操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.66,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好了 全力的上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:53.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我会全力以布的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:55.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,差不多要上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊…但是…我还没有心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:01.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月 你看那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.52,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸静呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸静不在啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.53,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,感谢今天来到现场的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:21.41,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,在这个漫天繁星的好日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.03,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这是结婚典礼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:25.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,完全迷失了自我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.95,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,说的是 但是不缺乏冲击力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:32.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是这是选举啊 这样不利 会落选的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.75,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那么 就让我施一计 巧借东风
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:38.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:42.05,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月的表演就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:50.31,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不过还是真是稀奇 静会肌肉酸痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:56.07,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,锻炼到能在舞台上连续跳一两个小时的静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.36,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,竟然因为和夏月训练受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:05.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,难得来了 一起唱一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:09.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.08,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,还在意那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.04,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,目前为止伤害了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:21.01,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你的光环是无法和他人融合的双刃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别害怕 放心的去唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.98,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月的光环可没那么弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.82,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,手牵起手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:42.74,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:43.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎呀 不想看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:44.78,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:49.49,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊 夏月 平时的干劲去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:55.58,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,新泻的大家 晚上好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:00.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,鬼丸静!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.51,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊 好好唱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.09,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,静小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:05.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是鬼丸小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:06.76,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:11.85,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,能保护大家的 只有我们楼凯党
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.39,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请为楼凯党的鹭宫投出一票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:16.81,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,女主角党?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:21.15,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,只会唱歌跳舞的偶像议员能做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.86,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,政治是力量 是安定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.61,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不能被她们蒙骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:29.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是鹭宫 请为我投票
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.87,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,交给我鹭宫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:38.00,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,保证让大家的生活更加富裕安康
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:42.59,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,各位的政治权利真正需要唱歌跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:46.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,不!绝对不是 真正需要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这光环…什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.02,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,啊 夏月碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.73,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哇 好美的光环
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.83,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,大家 我一定会让大家露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:41.25,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,所以请为我星菜夏月投上宝贵的一票
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:42.88,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:44.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.50,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好了 给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:49.72,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.88,0:20:50.47,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,夏月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.34,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别认输 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.35,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,这样你也是国会议员了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,加油啊 星菜议员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:05.69,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎哟 议员什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.40,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,别嬉皮笑脸的 正经点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:07.94,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.28,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:09.99,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:22.92,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,请说说成为议员现在的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.21,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,作为偶像议员 想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:30.30,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,那个…总之 我会全力以布的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.13,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 又咬舌头了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:40.89,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,虽然我们楼凯拥有会议过半的席位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:46.10,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,但是 就这样放纵偶像议员 怕是有后顾之忧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:48.48,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:51.32,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,马上就将她们碾碎
Comment: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:43.06,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,我是新泻县出身的偶像议员 星菜夏月
Comment: 0,0:23:43.26,0:23:46.64,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,有活动哟 DVD也在接受预订
Comment: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:48.14,Idol_Jihen_main,,0,0,0,,下回也会加留的!
